ygData.messageBody:
I play on the Solusek Ro server. I currently at level 22. The places I have
hunted so far : Qeynos, Qeynos Hills, Blackburrow, Everfrost, W.Karana,
Rivervale, Misty Thicket, Runneyeye, Gorge, Unrest and the Cauldron. I am now
back on the main land and am going to attend a wedding in E. Commons and then
I will be heading for S. Karana for hunting. I have never been there before
so it will be a new experience for me.
I have found that it is a long process to level most of the time. If I am
lucky I can do a level in one week but that is a rare exception and I also
like to bake so I have to take time to get the supplies for my cooking. I
also would like to begin the Paw Quest shortly as I have done the SSOL,
already. I am not sure about going for the Clerics armor. Have a great day!
Healingsun, Solusek Ro, level
22 cleric, Rodcet Nife
